# Diligent Design System Rules

## Source of Truth

- Figma file: **Diligent Shadcn** (`wJ4C33K2hKe0vGvKb8vVUL`)
- Stack: Vite + React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS v4 + ShadCN/UI
- Font: **Geist Variable** (loaded via `@fontsource-variable/geist`)

## Component Organization

- IMPORTANT: Always use components from `src/components/ui/` when possible
- Place new UI components in `src/components/ui/`
- Place feature/page components in `src/components/`
- Follow PascalCase for component names
- Components must accept a `className` prop for composition
- Use path alias `@/` for all imports (e.g. `@/components/ui/button`)

## Design Tokens — Colors

All colors are defined as CSS custom properties in `src/index.css`.
IMPORTANT: Never hardcode hex colors — always use the semantic token via Tailwind utility classes.

| Token                  | Light Value  | Tailwind Class              |
|------------------------|--------------|-----------------------------|
| `--background`         | `#ffffff`    | `bg-background`             |
| `--foreground`         | `#0f1113`    | `text-foreground`           |
| `--primary`            | `#1a1c1e`    | `bg-primary`, `text-primary`|
| `--primary-foreground` | `#ffffff`    | `text-primary-foreground`   |
| `--secondary`          | `#f9f9fc`    | `bg-secondary`              |
| `--secondary-foreground`| `#1a1c1e`  | `text-secondary-foreground` |
| `--muted`              | `#f0f0f3`    | `bg-muted`                  |
| `--muted-foreground`   | `#76777a`    | `text-muted-foreground`     |
| `--accent`             | `#f0f0f3`    | `bg-accent`                 |
| `--accent-foreground`  | `#0f1113`    | `text-accent-foreground`    |
| `--destructive`        | `#dc2626`    | `bg-destructive`            |
| `--border`             | `#e2e2e5`    | `border-border`             |
| `--input`              | `#e2e2e5`    | `border-input`              |
| `--ring`               | `#1a1c1e`    | `ring-ring`                 |

